{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_02_03",
  "title": "小美山愛",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_live-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさーん！　盛り上がってますかー！\nLizNoirは、全開でいきますよー！",
      "startTime": 5.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6333.333333333334,
          "startTime": 7.633333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブが始まったばかりなのに会場は凄い熱気だな\n愛も万全のコンディションで調子がよさそうだ",
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、このライブに来てくれたみなさんしか\n味わえない、初披露の楽曲もやりまーす！",
      "startTime": 21.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5233.333333333334,
          "startTime": 24.066666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "実はこの曲のためにずーっと緊張していたんですけど\nこうして莉央さんの背中を借りてたら安心してきました",
      "startTime": 32.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "もっともっと盛り上げていくから\n最後まで楽しんで下さいねー！",
      "startTime": 38.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4500,
          "startTime": 41.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "プレッシャーを感じていたのが嘘みたいに\n伸び伸びとパフォーマンスしているな",
      "startTime": 45.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今日のLizNoirはいつも以上に会場を\n沸かせてくれそうだ",
      "startTime": 51.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.333333333333,
          "startTime": 54.03333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_liz-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
